<figureCitation box="[1087,1172,1022,1045]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="13.[111,147,2060,2081]" captionTargetBox="[114,1449,1027,2017]" captionTargetId="figure-18@13.[97,1473,998,2046]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="Fig. 5. Form of the carapace and adult male chela of subgroups of the genus Macrophthalmus V: (a) subgenus Tasmanoplax and (b) subgenus Venitus. Scale bars = 5mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4508318" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4508318/files/figure.png" pageId="11" pageNumber="42">Fig. 5A</figureCitation>
